{"title": "Ground Water", "html": "<section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_small\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container has_text_color\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner us_custom_6df4bc3a \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h4><strong>Groundwater Level Monitoring Stations and Records</strong></h4>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><!-- Row Backgrounds --><div class=\"upb_color\" data-bg-override=\"0\" data-bg-color=\"#506677\" data-fadeout=\"\" data-fadeout-percentage=\"30\" data-parallax-content=\"\" data-parallax-content-sense=\"30\" data-row-effect-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-img-parallax-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-rtl=\"false\"  data-custom-vc-row=\"\"  data-vc=\"6.1\"  data-is_old_vc=\"\"  data-theme-support=\"\"   data-overlay=\"false\" data-overlay-color=\"\" data-overlay-pattern=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-opacity=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-size=\"\"    ></div><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_small\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>At present Sierra Leone does not have a national groundwater monitoring network and to our knowledge this has never existed. This page includes groundwater levels from hand-dug wells and boreholes which were monitored during the Water Security Project</h5>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_small with_line width_default thick_2 style_dashed color_primary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_auto\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h3>Key</h3>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_small\"></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>Site Reference Numbers</h5>\n<p>The site reference number prefix SN link back to Map 10, Rokel-Seli River Basin Water Security Project in the 2015 Water Security Report. This can be viewed on the <a href=\"/maps/\">maps</a> page of this site.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>Included Data</h5>\n<p>The types of data that are included in the downloads are indicated in the charts below as follows:</p>\n<p><strong>G</strong> Groundwater Level<br />\n<strong>R</strong> Rainfall<br />\n<strong>B</strong> Barometric Pressure<br />\n<strong>Tw</strong> Water Temperature<br />\n<strong>Ta</strong> Air Temperature</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>Data Owner, Collector or Origin</h5>\n<p>The data is made available from different sources which is listed in the charts below:</p>\n<p><strong>BWMA</strong> Bumbuna Watershed Management Authority<br />\n<strong>MWR</strong> Ministry of Water Resources</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_medium\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"